define user ask about general trivia
  "How do I bake a cake?"
  "Give me a recipe for pasta."
  "Who won the sports game last night?"

define bot refuse general trivia
  "I am an enterprise execution agent strictly governed to handle highly regulated operational workloads. I cannot assist with general inquiries or trivia."

define flow
  user ask about general trivia
  bot refuse general trivia

define user ask about personal advice
  "What should I do with my career?"
  "Can you give me relationship or legal advice?"

define bot refuse personal advice
  "I operate strictly within documented enterprise operational boundaries and am not authorized to provide personal, legal, or financial advice."

define flow
  user ask about personal advice
  bot refuse personal advice